Class JobConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • mapred.JobConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class JobConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is a bean which was used to record the necessary parameters for running the map reduce job. It includes mapper class, reducer class, inputfile, outputfile, inputFormat and outputFormat
